snippet.title: Undertale: Disbelief (Demo Released) - Trailer
snippet.description:
So, after a long time of waiting, we finally finished the demo for our Undertale fangame! We are so excited to finally share this with all of you. We hope you'll enjoy our demo, we worked very hard!
Download the demo here: https://gamejolt.com/games/disbelief/268091
(Click "Download" in the top of the screen)
Remember to follow our Gamejolt page for updates!


Song used in this trailer:
https://soundcloud.com/flamesatgames/undertale-disbelief-demo

Twitter:
https://twitter.com/FlamesAtGames

Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/FlamesAtGames
